did someone say my name?

02:19.219 --> 02:20.469
You got it.

02:25.102 --> 02:28.562
Fischer! Fischer!
Fischer! Fischer! Fischer!

02:42.366 --> 02:43.661
Thank you.

02:45.412 --> 02:47.454
You guys have it real easy.

02:48.748 --> 02:51.625
I never had it like this
where I grew up.

02:51.750 --> 02:55.170
But I send my kids here
because, the fact is,

02:55.254 --> 02:57.967
you go to one of the best
schools in the country:

02:58.466 --> 02:59.969
- Rushmore.
- Shh.

03:00.011 --> 03:02.137
Now, for some of you,

03:02.262 --> 03:04.388
it doesn't matter.

03:04.930 --> 03:08.142
You were born rich,
and you're going to stay rich.

03:08.851 --> 03:11.187
But here's my advice
to the rest of you:

03:12.771 --> 03:17.027
Take dead aim
on the rich boys.

03:17.193 --> 03:19.654
Get them
in the crosshairs...

03:19.696 --> 03:22.157
and take them down.

03:22.324 --> 03:26.450
Just remember:
They can buy anything,

03:26.533 --> 03:29.621
but they can't buy backbone.

03:29.746 --> 03:32.122
Don't let them forget that.

03:32.707 --> 03:34.418
Thank you.

03:41.634 --> 03:44.136
Free for graduation, Herman?
Perhaps you could give us an encore.

03:44.220 --> 03:46.678
- Nicholas! Copernicus!
- I don't give a shit.

03:46.720 --> 03:48.429
I paid for the whole damn natatorium.

03:48.512 --> 03:51.310
The least these little pricks
can do is hear me out.

03:51.393 --> 03:53.853
- Hi, Dr. Guggenheim.
- Hello, Max.

03:53.895 --> 03:55.980
Hello, I'm Max Fischer.

03:56.189 --> 04:00.400
