- Hello.

04:07.114 --> 04:10.662
Oh, Mr. Blume, this is my
chapel partner, Dirk Calloway.

04:10.745 --> 04:12.829
Nice to meet you, Dirk.

04:12.913 --> 04:14.873
Well, thanks.

04:19.209 --> 04:21.546
You know...

04:21.712 --> 04:25.007
I really think you're
right about Rushmore.

04:25.174 --> 04:27.217
Come on, Dirk.

04:29.554 --> 04:32.474
- What's his name again?
- Max Fischer.

04:33.724 --> 04:35.644
Sharp little guy.

04:38.229 --> 04:41.481
He's one of the worst
students we've got.

