01:29:41.532 --> 01:29:44.494
<i># The dressing rooms are gray #</i>

01:29:44.535 --> 01:29:47.581
<i># They come on strong
and it ain't too long #</i>

01:29:47.664 --> 01:29:50.792
<i># For they make you
feel a man #</i>

01:29:50.875 --> 01:29:53.960
<i># But love is blind
